bypasses.name: A-Bypass
bypasses.appNotes: Remember to enable tweak injection for `!ABypass2`.

bypasses.name: Shadow
bypasses.appNotes: Apply the recommended settings from the guide and enable `Lockdown Mode`.

bypasses.name: Hestia
bypasses.appNotes: Keep dlopen patches and compatibility mode disabled. Enable Image Check Patches, else app will crash.

bypasses.name: Liberty Lite (Beta)
bypasses.appNotes: Use Choicy **or** libhooker-configurator to allow injection for only `zzzzzLiberty`
